{"tid":904126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國FDA擬全國禁止薄荷味香煙","createTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T14:48:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb95c1024f6e22b625504cdde3c2a9e57f36388","tid":904126,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"美國食品及藥物管理局(FDA)擬禁止薄荷味香煙。<br />\n<br />\n由於薄荷香煙受到年輕及非洲裔煙民的歡迎，加上在香煙中加入薄荷醇，能緩和由吸煙引起的喉嚨刺激，因此更能吸引年輕人吸食。<br />\n<br />\n局方表示，正尋求在全國範圍內禁止薄荷味香煙及雪茄，但預期或需要超過1年的時間才能敲定，而要在市場上執行則還需1年時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外，局方亦對調味電子煙的銷售實施限制，將在未來幾個月生效，並會很快指示煙草公司將一些調味雪茄從市場上下架，而且正在制定一項單獨的規定，全面禁止調味雪茄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1993899/美國擬禁止薄荷味香煙\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1993899%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%96%84%E8%8D%B7%E5%91%B3%E9%A6%99%E7%85%99&d=38jqZUFrbngVAerxXx0BO5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=bfa4ac5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1993899/美國擬禁止薄荷味香煙</a>"},{"pid":"d802aa7bf251a0cfafad9af5c3e0b363724199dd","tid":904126,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"萬寶路成條line 都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe1b18e8b958c08a331b456df2bfb44130bc061","tid":904126,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"爆珠萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd95af54871f0e11051431806afa802fac7ae41","tid":904126,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abe1b18e8b958c08a331b456df2bfb44130bc061","tid":904126,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"爆珠萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"美國禁<br />\n又唔係其他地方禁"}]}